MO-MI, KELUAR DARI SANA SEKARANG!

463
00:41:19,226 --> 00:41:21,896
BAJINGAN ITU MAU MEMERKOSAMU!

464
00:41:28,611 --> 00:41:32,156
JU OH-NAM

465
00:41:41,165 --> 00:41:43,000
<i>Halo?</i>

466
00:41:43,709 --> 00:41:44,877
<i>Mo... Mo-mi!</i>

467
00:41:51,509 --> 00:41:54,136
Apa kau baik-baik saja, Mo-mi?

468
00:42:20,746 --> 00:42:22,665
Apa dia mati?

469
00:42:26,794 --> 00:42:28,128
Aku tidak tahu.

470
00:42:31,298 --> 00:42:32,883
Bajingan ini

471
00:42:33,842 --> 00:42:36,053
